videos.description: Zion Williamson goes up for a rebound and takes an elbow from Princeton's Myles Stephens before leaving the floor.
videos.headline: Zion takes elbow to mouth, leaves game

videos.description: Duke's Zion Williamson make an athletic layup off the assist from Tre  Jones.
videos.headline: Zion lays it in off lob from Jones

videos.description: Cameron Reddish steals the ball and throws it up to RJ Barrett, who flies high for a big-time dunk.
videos.headline: Reddish takes it away and finds Barrett, who slams it

videos.description: Zion Williamson gets up in the air and gets the big block on the Princeton layup attempt.
videos.headline: Zion gets way up there for the block

videos.description: RJ Barrett drops 27 points and Zion Williamson contributes 17 to help Duke clobber Princeton 101-50.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Williamson, Barrett lead Duke to huge win over Princeton) 2018/12/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williamson, Barrett lead Duke to huge win over Princeton
